    "• The Knowledge layer comprises a domain-specific model and training data, providing both domain-specific knowledge and data-derived insights.In the next section, we will provide a detailed description of how we implemented Human-AI Deliberation and Deliberative AI architecture in the context of a graduate admissions task.",
    "INSTANTIATING THE ARCHITECTURE: GRADUATE ADMISSION PREDICTION 4.1 Task, Dataset and AI ModelWe choose to use graduate admission as an illustrative task to demonstrate how to instantiate the proposed Human-AI Deliberation architecture.",
    "In this task, participants decide on admitting or rejecting applicants to a U.S. university based on their profiles.",
    "We chose this task for two key reasons.",
    "First, this task is widely used in AI-assisted decision-making research [23,34,135,138], with real-world universities employing AI algorithms for decision consistency and workload reduction [99,129]."
